  tiers:
  - title:
      en: Greek Spy
      native: Yunan Casusu
    maxPercentage: 12
    subtitle:
      en: "Nice try kom\u015Fu"
      native: "Yemezler kom\u015Fu"
    description:
      en: "You think Baklava is Greek, call Turkish coffee 'Greek coffee', and you
        drink tea from a mug (not a tulip glass). M\u0130T has been notified. Remain
        seated."
      native: "Baklavan\u0131n Yunan oldu\u011Funu san\u0131yorsun, T\xFCrk kahvesine
        'Yunan kahvesi' diyorsun ve \xE7ay\u0131 bardaktan de\u011Fil kupadan i\xE7iyorsun.
        M\u0130T'e haber verildi. Yerinde kal."
  - title:
      en: All-Inclusive Tourist
      native: "Her \u015Eey Dahil Turist"
    maxPercentage: 25
    subtitle:
      en: Very cheap very nice!
      native: "\xC7ok ucuz \xE7ok g\xFCzel!"
    description:
      en: You wear a Fez (nobody has worn one since 1925), you haggle at fixed-price
        stores, and you paid 500 Euros for a 50 Lira carpet. The Grand Bazaar sends
        its regards.
      native: "Fes tak\u0131yorsun (1925'ten beri kimse takm\u0131yor), sabit fiyatl\u0131
        d\xFCkkanlarda pazarl\u0131k yap\u0131yorsun ve 50 liral\u0131k hal\u0131ya
        500 Euro \xF6dedin. Kapal\u0131\xE7ar\u015F\u0131 selamlar\u0131n\u0131 iletiyor."
  - title:
      en: Erasmus Student
      native: "Erasmus \xD6\u011Frencisi"
    maxPercentage: 40
    subtitle:
      en: "\u015Eerefe Dostum!"
      native: "\u015Eerefe Dostum!"
    description:
      en: "You survive on 5 Lira d\xF6ner and Efes. You think Tarkan is a soap brand.
        You tried to pet a street cat and now you're feeding 12 of them."
      native: "5 liral\u0131k d\xF6ner ve Efes ile hayatta kal\u0131yorsun. Tarkan'\u0131n
        sabun markas\u0131 oldu\u011Funu san\u0131yorsun. Sokak kedisi sevmeye \xE7al\u0131\u015Ft\u0131n,
        \u015Fimdi 12 tanesini besliyorsun."
  - title:
      en: Average Citizen
      native: "Ortalama Vatanda\u015F"
    maxPercentage: 60
    subtitle:
      en: "Yapacak bir \u015Fey yok"
      native: "Yapacak bir \u015Fey yok"
    description:
      en: "You drink 15 \xE7ays a day (minimum). You honk 0.1 seconds after green.
        You can't have enouch of 3 lettered shops.You say 'in\u015Fallah' at least
        60 times a day."
      native: "G\xFCnde 15 \xE7ay i\xE7iyorsun (minimum). Ye\u015Filde 0.1 saniyede
        kornaya bas\u0131yorsun. 3 harfli marketlerden \xE7\u0131km\u0131yorsun.
        G\xFCnde en az 60 kez 'in\u015Fallah' diyorsun."
  - title:
      en: "Mahalle Day\u0131s\u0131"
      native: "Mahalle Day\u0131s\u0131"
    maxPercentage: 75
    subtitle:
      en: Professional Excavator Watcher
      native: "Profesyonel Kep\xE7e \u0130zleyicisi"
    description:
      en: "You can watch construction for 6 hours with hands behind your back. You
        know the tomato prices at 4 different pazars. You fix everything with WD-40
        and \xE7ay."
      native: "Ellerini arkada ba\u011Flay\u0131p 6 saat in\u015Faat izleyebilirsin.
        4 farkl\u0131 pazardaki domates fiyat\u0131n\u0131 biliyorsun. Her \u015Feyi
        WD-40 ve \xE7ayla tamir ediyorsun."
  - title:
      en: Teyze
      native: Teyze
    maxPercentage: 85
    subtitle:
      en: "Sen \xE7ok zay\u0131flam\u0131\u015Fs\u0131n"
      native: "Sen \xE7ok zay\u0131flam\u0131\u015Fs\u0131n"
    description:
      en: "You carry emergency b\xF6rek in your purse. You know everyone's business
        on the street. You pinch children's cheeks with the force of a hydraulic
        press."
      native: "\xC7antanda acil durum b\xF6re\u011Fi var. Sokaktaki herkesin i\u015Fini
        biliyorsun. \xC7ocuklar\u0131n yanaklar\u0131n\u0131 hidrolik pres g\xFCc\xFCyle
        s\u0131k\u0131yorsun."
  - title:
      en: "\xC7ay Oca\u011F\u0131 Ba\u015Fkan\u0131"
      native: "\xC7ay Oca\u011F\u0131 Ba\u015Fkan\u0131"
    maxPercentage: 94
    subtitle:
      en: "Koyu mu a\xE7\u0131k m\u0131?"
      native: "Koyu mu a\xE7\u0131k m\u0131?"
    description:
      en: Your blood type is turkish tea. You put yogurt even on pizza. You drive
        Istanbul to Ankara in 3 hours with hazard lights on the entire way.
      native: "Kan grubun do\u011Fu\u015F \xE7ay. Pizzaya bile yo\u011Furt koyuyorsun.
        \u0130stanbul'dan Ankara'ya 3 saatte, yol boyunca d\xF6rtl\xFClerle gidiyorsun."
  - title:
      en: Sultan of Simit
      native: "Simit Sultan\u0131"
    maxPercentage: 100
    subtitle:
      en: Afiyet olsun
      native: Afiyet olsun
    description:
      en: You have transcended Turkey; you are Turkey. Street cats follow you like
        a sultan. You finish every sentence with 'Allah korusun'. Tarkan has a poster
        of you.
      native: "T\xFCrkiye'nin \xF6tesine ge\xE7tin; sen T\xFCrkiye'sin. Sokak kedileri
        seni sultan gibi takip ediyor. Her c\xFCmleni 'Allah korusun' ile bitiriyorsun.
        Tarkan'\u0131n duvar\u0131nda senin posterin var."
